  * Applied patch to audio routing signal handling (Partial fix for NB#143242)
    | Patch provided by Janos Kovacs

 -- Pekka Lundstr√∂m <pekka.lundstrom@nokia.com>  Fri, 16 Oct 2009 15:15:20 +0300

